    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(center)"><placeName>Evergreen S.</placeName> in <add>?</add>
                <date>Nov: 1844</date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)"><addressee>Rev: I. Leeser</addressee>!</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Sir!<lb/> The postmaster of <placeName>Claiborne</placeName> to whom
                you <sic>adresset</sic> a note<lb/>
                <sic>presendet</sic> the same to me informing me that you hath not.<lb/> any
                prayerbooks according the german or polish rituals. <del>togh</del><lb/> Though
                preferring those, yet, I am not <sic>prejudicet</sic> to any<lb/> other
                    <sic>custome</sic>. You will therefore be so good to send me a<lb/> copy of the
                portuguese ritual with english translation<lb/> also a copy for <persName>Sanders
                    &amp; Co.</persName>
                <persName>Rothshild</persName> x <persName>Kayser</persName>,
                    <persName>Levy</persName> x<lb/>
                <persName>Hirshfeld</persName> all of <placeName>Claiborne</placeName> x a copy to
                    <persName>Meirs &amp; Co.</persName>
                <placeName>Luggsville<lb/> Clark County, Ala.</placeName> Those Gentlemen authorized
                me to inform<lb/> you, that they deem it not necessary to subscribe for the<lb/>
                first <sic>volum</sic> of the occident having already read my copy,<lb/> You will
                also please send me 3 hebrew spelling books,<lb/> also a copy of the „voice of
                Jacob„ for which I intend<lb/> to subscribe for hereafter. Please send the bill with
                the<lb/> books which amount. shall be <sic>remittet</sic> without delay!</p>
            <p>Respecty.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Your obt</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <persName role="author">BHEmanuel</persName>
            </p>
            <p>NB. Please <sic>rimit</sic> the books<lb/> to <placeName>Claiborne
                Ala.</placeName></p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>Evergreen Ala</placeName>
                <hi rend="indent(4)">Paid 25</hi>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(4)"><date>Nov. 14</date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">Rev: I. <hi rend="underline"><addressee>Leeser</addressee></hi></p>
            <p rend="indent(4)"><hi rend="underline">Editor</hi> of the <hi rend="underline"
                    >Occident</hi> &amp; american</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">jewish <sic>Atvocat</sic></p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <placeName>No. 118 <hi rend="underline">Southforth St.</hi></placeName>
            </p>
